d":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"都係二三架啦 <br />\n<br />\n利申睇完公立拎醫生信出去買機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:05:47.000Z","msg":"我都想睇公立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />排到2022"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"公立要排睡眠測試有排你等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:49:01.000Z","msg":"係，佢都講到話無了期 我仲要東區 好似得一間房"},{"pid":"29ab55a7384fe41133e242a00356430015ca48bb","tid":2509510,"uid":74185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:50:53.000Z","msg":"我想問都最尾其實係咪都係用呼吸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係我求奇搵間公司test完就買部機算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇私家我驚好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef71032fb03b09f1178f229dcbf088398ad73cc","tid":2509510,"uid":219538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:56:36.000Z","msg":"私家一定最快，保險有得claim就私家<br />\n門疹... 做test 所有費用我都claim到<br />\n呼吸機就無了"},{"pid":"ea6faefc7ac80371fe38c7e1d9e95a4759d4bf14","tid":2509510,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bb9605feb9d3752493d3bc6a80b30ee2178a22","tid":2509510,"uid":315645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21:58:02.000Z","msg":"身形算唔算肥胖"},{"pid":"9ce46833d05ef306951a6ff5cc8190a279397820","tid":2509510,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec696092456eca3c6fe5012c855bdea5a36104c","tid":2509510,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"買醫生膠紙<br />\n封住個口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:04:09.000Z","msg":"係，封住個口或者用下巴頭cool都有用，其實最主要係打開口瞓覺搞到嗰個肌肉封住左呼吸。"},{"pid":"47b93018a883f929ec177e68bcd413610af391a0","tid":2509510,"uid":63119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:13:52.000Z","msg":"如果有醫保就睇相關既耳鼻喉科，叫醫生寫紙去私院做test，之後醫生再話你知個case係乜問題。<br />\n呢類test其實係自己屋企都做得，都係會有人上門set儀器，唔複雜唔多野既。<br />\n銅鑼灣廣場一期有間專賣呼吸機，可以上去睇下問下。<br />\nbtw次次上去都見個姐姐仔條裙短到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e17b04f646d61bd48c11d7381845702620ed30","tid":2509510,"uid":53668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:30:08.000Z","msg":"買呼吸機最直接，價錢由幾仟蚊到萬幾元<br />\n睡眠窒息症會影響心臟同腎臟，要注意啦"},{"pid":"1a3b8d34ab58c84050c04431a3c27ed0df354829","tid":2509510,"uid":283418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:36:53.000Z","msg":"睡眠窒息症分三級，高中低，大小不一嘅型號，我測過2次，結果係中至高，由於孤寒及年紀大亦已退休，所以不用呼吸機，有租用及買斷方式，建議先租用，試到合適才買下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e73ef94c0e60757000fd80d072a67117402041","tid":2509510,"uid":47500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:44:26.000Z","msg":"用左呼吸機真係好訓好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9c45ebc90f910bd3f4cd36488c27bfde9fb1c2","tid":2509510,"uid":38819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"如果係，係咪要用一世？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf72fe915a566d753b2d351bb42e208e764857e7","tid":2509510,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"之前有間野有得響屋企度做<br />\n然後再比專科醫生睇指數寫報告<br />\n不過響屋企做一樣要駁好多儀器"},{"pid":"7c7f5bfe0d32c3aedd246216c9bd09d826994235","tid":2509510,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"打側訓"},{"pid":"dafbb8bf4e82def2299f5d6a6aa7015c460f8273","tid":2509510,"uid":74185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea6faefc7ac80371fe38c7e1d9e95a4759d4bf14","tid":2509510,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T21: